(22, 'U1 L1: Family and Home', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Family and Home</strong> introduces young learners to family roles, traditions, and the meaning of home.</p></li><li><p>Includes engaging activities: family tree drawing, sharing special traditions, and creating a home collage or picture.</p></li><li><p>Encourages interactive classroom discussions and reflection, concluding with a review and a class family song.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 627, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756474800857-6f2b4fce-c6bb-4295-898a-64def4bc2c0d.pptx', 'SS_G1_U1_L1_MN_V1.3.pptx', 8726783, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756475981335-7123d817-fbb1-4d4b-86fe-0dc9e7b806dc.png', 'published', 6, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 06:40:01', '2025-09-09 01:20:26', 151),
(23, 'U1 L2: My School and My Friends', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>School and Friends</strong> helps students explore the importance of school, classroom spaces, rules, and friendship.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: drawing the school, role-playing school rules, and creating a “Friendship Flower.”</p></li><li><p>Promotes teamwork, kindness, and understanding of school life through engaging visuals and collaborative tasks.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 627, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756475312340-446adc03-5814-42e1-85b0-11bffbbf64f7.pptx', 'SS_G1_U1_L2_MN_V1.3.pptx', 4995811, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756475312367-bb54d25b-aaf3-4aba-a67c-f3048e2243b3.png', 'published', 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 06:48:32', '2025-09-03 02:42:38', 150),
(24, 'U1 L3: My Community Helpers', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Community Helpers</strong> introduces students to important roles such as doctor, teacher, police, firefighter, sanitation worker, and construction worker.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: design your own helper badge, play a circle time game, and write a thank-you note.</p></li><li><p>Encourages values of gratitude, respect, and responsibility, while helping students understand how helpers keep communities safe and strong.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 627, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756475608786-2542e998-4af6-44d0-beab-9ab910cb6694.pptx', 'SS_G1_U1_L3.pptx', 4053562, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756475608807-868af400-ad73-4892-859f-9db24eea8884.png', 'published', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 06:53:28', '2025-09-02 05:47:54', 149),
(27, 'U2 L1: Our Country, Saudi Arabia', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Saudi Arabia</strong> introduces students to the country’s history, leaders, land, neighbors, and major regions.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: locating Saudi Arabia on a map, sharing travel experiences, coloring the flag, and singing together.</p></li><li><p>Promotes national pride, respect, and love for the homeland through engaging classroom experiences.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 627, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756529749695-fc8dc444-5acf-4a68-9912-b25f808784ef.pptx', 'SS_G1_U2_L1.pptx', 6212562, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756529749727-4e5bf327-2931-4b79-b6db-ecab5776758f.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 21:55:49', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 148),
(28, 'U2 L2: Saudi Arabia and Its People', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Important Places in</strong> <strong>Saudi Arabia</strong> introduces students to the holy cities of Makkah and Madinah, as well as the capital city Riyadh.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: drawing and coloring the Kaaba, a city landmark match-up game, and creating a Saudi City Passport.</p></li><li><p>Promotes respect for holy places, awareness of important landmarks, and love for the country.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 627, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756531992829-217ea222-6288-46ae-9efe-592e5b41e45c.pptx', 'SS_G1_U2_L2.pptx', 7140363, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756531992867-2f3f801e-0c43-4137-abe7-49a20229cecf.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 22:33:12', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 147),
(29, 'U2 L3: Saudi Heroes', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Saudi Heroes</strong> introduces students to King Abdulaziz as the founding father and highlights his leadership in unifying the nation.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: creating a Leader’s Crown, reflecting on leadership qualities, and using a “Leadership Mirror” to see themselves as leaders.</p></li><li><p>Promotes values of courage, responsibility, kindness, and honesty while encouraging students to recognize their own leadership potential.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 627, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756533147380-5707cef8-f547-43f3-825e-55cfcb53d0f1.pptx', 'SS_G1_U2_L3.pptx', 4530424, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756533147403-48ce3960-1f28-43ea-9190-be7b08b47c40.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 22:52:27', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 146),
(30, 'U3 L1: Landforms and Water', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Landforms and Water</strong> introduces students to deserts, mountains, plateaus, oceans, rivers, lakes, and the Red Sea.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: building a landform diorama, key vocabulary exploration, a right-or-wrong game, and a nature walk.</p></li><li><p>Promotes environmental awareness, care for natural resources, and curiosity about the land and water bodies around us.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 627, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756533474563-227b079b-70b8-485e-830a-46b51ac7aef9.pptx', 'SS_G1_U3_L1.pptx', 9270199, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756533474818-fa4fc937-4868-409e-baa1-c33a24ab6cb4.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 22:57:54', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 145),
(31, 'U3 L2: Taking Care of Our World', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Taking Care of Our World</strong> introduces students to the importance of clean air, water, and homes, along with the principles of reduce, reuse, and recycle.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Recycling Station Challenge, Good vs. Bad Actions game, and the Green Hands Pledge for planting trees.</p></li><li><p>Promotes environmental responsibility, kindness to nature and animals, and Islamic values of cleanliness and care for the Earth.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 627, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756533537640-1cd47890-42ea-4f36-889b-654f5bfa15c2.pptx', 'SS_G1_U3_L2.pptx', 11445113, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756533538189-fc7bd893-4d31-42d7-932b-61134f6be72f.png', 'draft', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 22:58:58', '2025-09-03 06:16:26', 144),
(32, 'U4 L1: What We Need and What We Want', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Needs and Wants</strong> helps students understand the difference between essential needs, such as food, water, shelter, clothing, and clean air, and non-essential wants like toys, ice cream, and video games.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: sorting game on needs vs. wants, creating a Gratitude Jar, and a story session <em>“The Boy Who Only Wanted Toys.”</em></p></li><li><p>Promotes thankfulness to God, awareness of smart choices, and appreciation for life’s essentials.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 627, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756533696752-4a7a4b4a-6878-416f-8cdf-6ea7e6e0e5f0.pptx', 'SS_G1_U4_L1.pptx', 8345349, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756533696879-8adf687d-eca9-41d2-a516-b1fba9b3dd19.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 23:01:36', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 143),
(33, 'U4 L2: Money and Fairness', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Money and Fairness</strong> introduces students to the concept of money, trade, markets, and the importance of honesty in buying and selling.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: classroom mini-market role play, market scene coloring, and a story on honesty.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of needs vs. wants, fairness in trade, and Islamic values of honesty.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 627, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756533770299-7d7f95cd-6785-45c1-aca8-6b98e23e215d.pptx', 'SS_G1_U4_L2.pptx', 15392393, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756533771386-d200f168-698d-4a9a-af26-344542328150.png', 'published', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 23:02:51', '2025-09-30 07:04:40', 142),
(34, 'U4 L3: Sharing and Helping Others', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Sharing and Helping Others</strong> introduces students to the meaning of sharing, the concept of Zakat, and everyday ways to help others.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Sharing Circle Time, One Good Deed a Day calendar, and a story on the Prophet’s (PBUH) kindness.</p></li><li><p>Promotes kindness, charity, and Islamic values of helping and caring for others.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 627, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756533824455-753a6dac-9ca2-43c0-a704-2f8cc20c3994.pptx', 'SS_G1_U4_L3.pptx', 5993829, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756533824475-36e8367e-933e-4a90-9d2c-73496ea008a9.png', 'published', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 23:03:44', '2025-09-30 06:59:33', 141),
(35, 'U1 L1: My Neighborhood and Community Helpers', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Neighborhood and Community Helpers</strong> introduces students to important places such as parks, markets, schools, and hospitals, and the roles of helpers who work there.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: pointing out neighborhood places, designing a helper’s badge, guessing community helpers, and role-playing responsible actions.</p></li><li><p>Promotes responsibility, awareness of community spaces, and respect for helpers.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 628, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756535660387-ce7ae79b-07de-4985-91fe-6eef0b1a4b76.pptx', 'SS_G2_U1_L1.pptx', 13154435, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756535661177-5abb8f0e-c500-4839-9215-4b88e0527f98.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 23:34:21', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 140),
(36, 'U1 L2: My City', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>My</strong> <strong>Cities</strong> introduces students to the differences between villages, towns, and cities, and explains what makes cities special.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: picture identification, Word Explorer puzzle, naming traffic light colors, and a “Good Citizen” class chant.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of city life, the importance of rules, and responsibility in keeping cities clean and safe.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 628, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756535748120-0385585e-0459-4141-abf3-e39fb6455942.pptx', 'SS_G2_U1_L2.pptx', 11513185, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756535748681-4ca5451e-bce6-4386-b994-822db9bc1c4c.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-29 23:35:48', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 139),
(42, 'U1 L3: Important Places in Saudi Arabia', '<ul><li><p></p></li></ul><ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Important Places in Saudi Arabia</strong> introduces students to Makkah, Madinah, Riyadh, Al-Ula, Jeddah, and Al-Khobar, highlighting their religious, cultural, and historical importance.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Pin the City, drawing Elephant Rock in Al-Ula, and a chanting activity about Jeddah and Al-Khobar.</p></li><li><p>Promotes pride in Saudi heritage, respect for holy cities, and awareness of cultural landmarks.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 628, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756540410715-019e2b7e-7640-4e48-be8a-beaaed8869bc.pptx', 'SS_G2_U1_L3.pptx', 4912491, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756540410746-ef021500-e841-4504-858e-cf6bf8713b37.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 00:53:30', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 138),
(43, 'U2 L1: The Flag of Saudi Arabia', '<p></p><ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>The Flag of Saudi Arabia</strong> explains the meaning of its colors, symbols, and inscription, including the Shahada as the Islamic declaration of faith.</p></li><li><p>Includes discussions on flag etiquette, the role of the sword as a symbol of justice and strength, and the green color representing peace and Islam.</p></li><li><p>Promotes national pride, respect for symbols of faith, and care for the country’s identity.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 628, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756540485149-4e2908a9-1da8-47e7-90c1-62b863fcca60.pptx', 'SS_G2_U2_L1.pptx', 2592052, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756540485168-2455a84d-19aa-433a-afc9-8a3370eb0b69.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 00:54:45', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 137),
(44, 'U2 L2: Saudi National Day', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Saudi National Day</strong> introduces students to the unification of the country by King Abdulaziz in 1932 and the significance of September 23.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: finding three green items in the classroom or on screen, and reflecting on symbols of unity and pride.</p></li><li><p>Promotes national identity, unity, and pride in Saudi Arabia’s history and achievements.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 628, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756540618693-9febf8ca-c613-47c1-8153-fe560ce1e3c3.pptx', 'SS_G2_U2_L2.pptx', 10828874, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756540619158-f5b877fc-ca01-4642-996e-87adbf3ad560.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 00:56:59', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 136),
(45, 'U2 L3: Leaders of Saudi Arabia', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on the <strong>Leaders of Saudi Arabia</strong> introduces King Abdulaziz as the unifier of the nation and highlights the role of the present leaders in modernization and Vision 2030.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: drawing someone who gives advice, imagining themselves as leaders, and designing leadership plans.</p></li><li><p>Promotes respect for national leaders, understanding of good leadership traits, and encourages students to practice responsibility and care in their own lives.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 628, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756540715762-80464aef-9bd6-472c-9c12-cb2a45793e89.pptx', 'SS_G2_U2_L3.pptx', 4810645, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756540715780-852b20ef-e320-4f11-8588-b2fbc75c44a0.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 00:58:35', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 135),
(46, 'U3 L1: Understanding the Land Around Us', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>The Land Around Us</strong> introduces students to deserts, mountains, seas, and oases, with examples from Saudi Arabia such as Ad-Dahna, Rub\' al Khali, and An Nafud.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: desert riddles and identifying features of different landforms.</p></li><li><p>Promotes curiosity about geography, awareness of natural features, and appreciation of Saudi Arabia’s unique landscapes.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 628, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756542137819-30eac5a2-a4b5-4cf5-9c1f-859254e09b92.pptx', 'SS_G2_U3_L1.pptx', 8611070, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756542137988-1477927a-10af-4cd4-b3c6-4f81874f543b.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:22:18', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 134),
(47, 'U3 L2: Weather and Seasons in Saudi Arabia', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Weather and Seasons in Saudi Arabia</strong> explains daily weather changes such as sun, rain, clouds, and wind, and introduces the four seasons.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Season Dress-Up Game, My Season Drawing, and a 7-Day Weather Journal Starter.</p></li><li><p>Promotes observation skills, awareness of seasonal changes, and appreciation of how weather affects daily life.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 628, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756542212980-94efd553-6774-4b5e-943c-3fe982d7308d.pptx', 'SS_G2_U3_L2.pptx', 6798798, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756542213012-7d22260d-e139-4b14-993b-67d1ecba2db7.png', 'draft', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:23:33', '2025-09-04 06:01:08', 133),
(48, 'U3 L3: Taking Care of Our Environment', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Taking Care of Our Environment</strong> explains the importance of air, water, land, animals, and people, and why protecting them is essential.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: My Environment Drawing, Identify Good and Bad actions, Do or Don’t Sorting, and an environmental chanting activity.</p></li><li><p>Promotes responsibility, Islamic values of cleanliness, and habits of conservation at home and school.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 628, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756542280679-6730e704-a594-46c9-8528-99d91d6ac72b.pptx', 'SS_G2_U3_L3.pptx', 5346719, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756542280701-944dc947-dcdd-45b2-addd-f3b3769f3a95.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:24:40', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 132),
(49, 'U4 L1: What Do We Need and What Do We Want?', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Needs and Wants</strong> helps students understand the difference between essential needs like food, water, clothes, and shelter, and non-essential wants.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Needs and Wants sorting, Draw a Smart Choice, and Gratitude Circle sharing.</p></li><li><p>Promotes responsibility, gratitude, and making wise choices in daily life.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 628, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756542328251-9a3af2df-55fd-4bc6-8e38-131ee0ce6a41.pptx', 'SS_G2_U4_L1.pptx', 4133231, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756542328267-886c53df-c143-430b-93f0-83e4148c45fb.png', 'published', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:25:28', '2025-09-30 07:01:25', 131),
(50, 'U4 L2: Helping Others in Need', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Helping Others in Need</strong> introduces the uses of money—saving, spending, and charity—and explains the importance of helping those with less.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Match the Action game and Plan Your Act of Kindness drawing task.</p></li><li><p>Promotes kindness, generosity, and understanding of charity and Zakat as part of Islamic values.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 628, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756542372287-35fc8495-002d-4658-96c6-607552d6e902.pptx', 'SS_G2_U4_L2.pptx', 4911941, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756542372315-c9bec830-c764-4f15-9a4e-b5c4c3cd19f7.png', 'published', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:26:12', '2025-09-30 07:04:52', 130),
(51, 'U1 L1: The Tapestry of Saudi Cultures', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Saudi Cultures</strong> introduces students to the traditions of different regions, including Najd, Asir, Hejaz, and the Eastern Province, with examples of clothing, food, and festivals.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Regional Dress-Up Day, Create Your Regional Food Menu, and Saudi Culture Travel Poster.</p></li></ul><p>Promotes pride in cultural diversity, appreciation of hospitality, and awareness of Islamic values in traditions</p>', 366, 436, 629, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756543055995-9315abfb-e35f-44c8-9147-dd8d3efd3bab.pptx', 'SS_G3_U1_L1.pptx', 15178252, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756543057053-0f33dc07-e238-4456-b97f-b6b521c5f3b3.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:37:37', '2025-09-02 01:56:31', 9),
(52, 'U1 L2: Festivals and Traditions', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Festivals and Traditions</strong> introduces students to Eid al-Fitr, Eid al-Adha, Saudi National Day, Hajj, and regional festivals such as the Taif Rose Festival and Souk Okaz.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Eid card making, Hajj journey map, Saudi Festival Travel Brochure, and Dates Tasting with fact-finding.</p></li><li><p>Promotes cultural pride, understanding of Islamic practices, and appreciation of national and regional celebrations.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 629, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756543153962-af5b1923-ce71-49e6-ad37-d633737e6f92.pptx', 'SS_G3_U1_L2.pptx', 12628133, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756543154670-fbbd879c-91ea-47cf-950f-18154df48dd7.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:39:14', '2025-09-02 01:56:31', 8),
(53, 'U1 L3: Contributions of Islamic Culture', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Islamic Culture</strong> introduces key contributions to science, medicine, philosophy, engineering, and art by scholars such as Ibn al-Haytham, Ibn Sina, Ibn Rushd, Al-Jazari, and Al-Farghani.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Scholar Trading Cards, Islamic Invention Timeline, Mini \"House of Wisdom,\" and exploring Islamic art and calligraphy.</p></li><li><p>Promotes pride in Islamic heritage, appreciation of knowledge, and awareness of lasting cultural contributions.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 629, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756543246952-d31e65f1-f20a-4942-99dd-609dbefb5ee3.pptx', 'SS_G3_U1_L3.pptx', 16559265, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756543248200-267c39ba-4361-4670-9979-ff29039256ae.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:40:48', '2025-09-02 01:56:31', 7),
(54, 'U2 L1: Exploring Our Land', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Saudi Arabia’s Land</strong> introduces major landforms, including deserts, mountains, and escarpments, along with water sources and natural resources.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Desert Animal Fact Cards, Landform Collage, and Water Conservation Pledge Poster.</p></li><li><p>Promotes appreciation of natural resources, awareness of water conservation, and understanding of Allah’s blessings in Saudi Arabia’s geography.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 629, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756543558691-3c619f7c-858b-4fd4-b9cd-fe10e1bb926a.pptx', 'SS_G3_U2_L1.pptx', 23871379, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756543560936-a3db90de-10bb-4f7a-8e9c-a0bf69a95687.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:46:00', '2025-09-02 01:56:31', 6),
(55, 'U2 L2: Water, Our Precious Resource', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Water in Saudi Arabia</strong> explains why water is important, where it comes from, and how it is used in farming, homes, and factories.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Build a Desalination Model, Water Saver Pledge Chain, and Water Walk Simulation.</p></li><li><p>Promotes responsibility in water conservation, awareness of farming techniques like drip irrigation, and appreciation of water as a vital resource.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 629, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756543683059-ad0b7c15-472b-41cb-9b46-74aa52b3f6c7.pptx', 'SS_G3_U2_L2.pptx', 17414331, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756543684423-c0c6fa4c-6ef8-4631-b67f-6a2cbadfb575.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:48:04', '2025-09-02 01:56:31', 5),
(56, 'U2 L3: Continents and Oceans', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Continents and Oceans</strong> introduces the seven continents and five oceans, explaining their features, weather, and sea life.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: My Continent Booklet, Fun Fact exploration, and Global Sharing Circle discussions.</p></li><li><p>Promotes global awareness, understanding of interdependence, and recognition of Saudi Arabia’s role in the world.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 629, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756543793597-ddcdfaa9-41c7-4635-ada8-f8b5c5415bb8.pptx', 'SS_G3_U2_L3.pptx', 15245789, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756543794665-c34ea71f-500f-4976-86b7-654f1cef183d.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:49:54', '2025-09-02 01:56:31', 4),
(57, 'U3 L1: What Is Government?', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Government</strong> introduces students to what a government is, its role in building services, and how it ensures fairness and safety through Islamic values.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Design a Leader’s Badge, Write Together task, Build a Mini Majlis, and Fairness Check Game.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of leadership, respect for Saudi Arabia’s system, and values of fairness, honesty, and consultation (Shura).</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 629, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756543881572-2f68b803-f5c7-4067-8164-5d0cf57b1cc4.pptx', 'SS_G3_U3_L1.pptx', 7189397, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756543881599-a2251492-f1a0-493c-b6aa-d1aa1cf7f914.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:51:21', '2025-09-02 01:56:31', 3),
(58, 'U3 L2: Introduction to Economics', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Economics</strong> introduces students to trade, goods and services, supply and demand, and how economics connects people locally and globally.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Buyer and Seller Role-Play, My Trade List Booklet, Supply and Demand Toy Game, and Trade Trail Map of Saudi Arabia.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of local and global trade, awareness of Saudi Arabia’s role in world markets, and Islamic values of fairness in trade.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 629, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756543966596-68900b5b-6cf6-4499-8473-28551dbb97b3.pptx', 'SS_G3_U3_L2.pptx', 20386190, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756543968362-25cf034c-e767-4fc3-b44f-8d147dae5130.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:52:48', '2025-09-02 01:56:37', 2),
(59, 'U3 L3: Celebrating Our Diversity', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Diversity</strong> introduces students to differences in food, languages, clothes, and celebrations, and explains how inclusive communities welcome and respect everyone.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Cultural Celebration Collage, Diversity Tree, Tradition Show-and-Tell, and “Say Hello” in different languages.</p></li><li><p>Promotes kindness, respect, inclusion, and appreciation of cultural traditions.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 629, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756544129204-9c97c1bc-1af4-404b-a92a-f4489210631e.pptx', 'SS_G3_U3_L3.pptx', 9761012, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756544129529-8d0e1179-7e0e-4131-aa81-3191f1c5c6bb.png', 'published', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:55:29', '2025-09-30 07:01:36', 1),
(60, 'U1 L1: Saudi Arabia’s Historical Connections', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Saudi Arabia’s Historical Connections</strong> introduces students to ancient trade routes such as the Red Sea Route, Silk Road, and Incense Route, and their role in connecting cultures.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Packing Challenge, Mini Map Marking, and Quick Think-Pair-Share discussions.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of cultural exchange, respect, and how trade shaped Saudi Arabia’s growth and influence in history.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 630, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756544281623-a9de4f17-ac59-4abe-a935-547994d8604e.pptx', 'SS_G4_U1_L1.pptx', 4222377, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756544281636-ec5c5610-5520-4b22-9639-e4862a55f714.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:58:01', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 120),
(61, 'U1 L2: Global Geography and Saudi Arabia', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Global Geography</strong> introduces students to Saudi Arabia’s location in Asia, its position on a peninsula, and its surrounding seas.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Draw &amp; Label Saudi Arabia map, Point the Direction exercise, and Neighbor Match-Up Game.</p></li><li><p>Promotes map-reading skills, awareness of neighboring countries, and understanding of Saudi Arabia’s geographic importance.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 630, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756544370175-829c28a4-402e-40c0-9838-b21547b0ec2a.pptx', 'SS_G4_U1_L2.pptx', 3684280, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756544370186-2bd221e1-6c34-4165-8f8b-3fe594290419.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 01:59:30', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 119),
(62, 'U1 L3: Governance and Global Cooperation', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Governance and Global Cooperation</strong> introduces students to governance in daily life and the role of international organizations in solving world problems.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Governance in Daily Life task, Think-Pair-Share on helping others, and discussions on key organizations like the UN, WHO, UNICEF, WTO, and Red Crescent.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of global cooperation, respect for international efforts, and understanding of Saudi Arabia’s role in global partnerships.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 630, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756544568571-8522d4cb-2b40-4f79-b407-6e64092a2431.pptx', 'SS_G4_U1_L3.pptx', 10706086, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756544569022-847b5459-4927-4ef9-af7e-7ad13f27ea16.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:02:49', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 118),
(63, 'U2 L1: Cultural Contributions', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Cultural Contributions</strong> introduces students to Saudi Arabia’s legacy through scholars like Ibn Khaldun and Imam Ahmad ibn Hanbal, as well as artistic contributions, past and present.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Scholar Snapshots, Artistic Eyes comparison, and reflections on Saudi Arabia’s global cultural influence.</p></li><li><p>Promotes pride in Saudi heritage, appreciation of Islamic scholarship, and recognition of traditional and modern artistic achievements.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 630, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756544813676-9ede83a7-07c4-4717-ae30-7b9d11b37fca.pptx', 'SS_G4_U2_L1.pptx', 3983212, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756544813704-e8f3a330-a132-405d-92f5-7973ec1cca28.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:06:53', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 117),
(64, 'U2 L2: Trade and Economic Contributions', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Trade and Economy</strong> introduces students to Saudi Arabia’s role as a top oil producer, its membership in OPEC, and the uses of oil in daily life.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: “What If Oil Stopped?” scenario, Match the Export game, and Economic Pillars task.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of Saudi Arabia’s global economic role, the importance of oil, and understanding of trade beyond oil.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 630, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756544927226-3f597c38-4784-4adf-8a4a-3a1233050799.pptx', 'SS_G4_U2_L2.pptx', 3446888, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756544927246-e934c1b8-1105-4936-9f5b-cd3a22dc249e.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:08:47', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 116),
(65, 'U2 L3: Vision 2030 and the Future', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Vision 2030</strong> introduces the three pillars - Ambitious Nation, Vibrant Society, and Thriving Economy, and how they guide Saudi Arabia’s future.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Future Planner, Pillar Match, and Build Your Dream City project.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of sustainability, innovation, eco-tourism, and pride in Saudi Arabia’s future while preserving culture.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 630, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756545055490-91de03e6-1ba5-41cd-a558-161ed4ec7659.pptx', 'SS_G4_U2_L3.pptx', 7100035, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756545055532-53fa78c6-54ff-4ae7-9204-45570a824478.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:10:55', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 115),
(66, 'U3 L1: What Is Global Citizenship?', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Global Citizenship</strong> introduces students to the idea of the world as one family, showing how people are connected through cooperation, cultures, and shared responsibilities.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Pass the Globe, Crisis Heroes role-play, World Culture Hunt, Saudi Pride Postcard, and Global Citizenship Oath.</p></li><li><p>Promotes respect for cultures, pride in Saudi traditions, global responsibility, and caring for the Earth.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 630, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756546709733-75f9c4e3-c54e-4a92-9432-3382706ae5a4.pptx', 'SS_G4_U3_L1.pptx', 2982642, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756546709758-501fee24-3c5b-4f1c-9ae6-250b3a7b19aa.png', 'draft', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:38:29', '2025-09-02 01:51:00', 114),
(67, 'U3 L2: Saudi Arabia in the Global Community', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Saudi Arabia in the Global Community</strong> highlights initiatives such as the Saudi Green Initiative, KS Relief humanitarian efforts, and desalination projects for clean water.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Grow a Tree poster, Water Saver Mission, and My Global Promise pledge.</p></li><li><p>Promotes environmental care, global responsibility, and pride in Saudi Arabia’s role in helping other nations.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 630, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756546853871-438e254b-5f96-4644-93c8-858fd13afd2a.pptx', 'SS_G4_U3_L2.pptx', 978110, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756546853878-5c8d7b78-b10e-4ace-867e-9761fbc4705f.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:40:53', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 113),
(68, 'U3 L3: Connecting with the World', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Connecting with the World</strong> explores how technology, travel, and communication bring people together and help cultures share ideas and traditions.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Global Connections Brainstorm, Digital World Icon Match, Stand &amp; Share reflection, group quiz, and Global Connector Badge design.</p></li><li><p>Promotes cultural exchange, digital literacy, and pride in Saudi Arabia’s role in sharing its culture with the world.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 630, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756546986989-dc49650c-927f-4b70-b3cb-82c038f885c3.pptx', 'SS_G4_U3_L3.pptx', 8732661, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756546987173-bf1b29be-da1d-4c55-8852-056494246684.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:43:07', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 112),
(69, 'U1 L1: Mesopotamia – The Cradle of Civilization', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Mesopotamia</strong> introduces the world’s first known civilization, its cities, farming systems, laws, and cultural achievements.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Civilization Sorting Game, My First Symbol design, and My Fair Rule tablet.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of early societies, innovations in farming and irrigation, and the importance of fairness through Hammurabi’s Code.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 631, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756547110613-cb6e8840-f37a-4364-b858-2fe54bce6dbb.pptx', 'SS_G5_U1_L1.pptx', 9778913, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756547110934-90ff0e68-78d1-4562-bbad-672668963b93.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:45:10', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 111),
(70, 'U1 L2: Ancient Egypt – Life Along the Nile', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Ancient Egypt</strong> explores the role of the Nile River in farming, trade, and city development, along with pyramids, monuments, and social structure.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: “What’s on My Farm?” drawing task and “My Role in Society” reflection.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of irrigation, teamwork in society, and appreciation of Egypt’s cultural and architectural legacy.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 631, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756547209457-f7ab748d-1907-4ba0-b6f2-a7d3806a87f6.pptx', 'SS_G5_U1_L2.pptx', 11209776, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756547209978-3efe0f23-5a50-43d9-80e9-2c98d9329db5.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:46:49', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 110),
(71, 'U1 L3: Ancient Trade and Cultural Exchanges', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Ancient Trade</strong> explains how trade routes like the Silk Road, Incense Route, Spice Route, and Trans-Saharan Route connected civilizations across Asia, Africa, Arabia, and Europe.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Trade Talk role-play, Guess the Good quiz, and Pack Your Camel drawing task.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of goods, ideas, and religions exchanged through trade, and appreciation of peaceful cultural connections in history.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 631, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756547375832-02d6f0f5-5769-421a-826b-3f558fb727ed.pptx', 'SS_G5_U1_L3.pptx', 2724061, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756547375843-ade43946-e5d0-4172-a2c1-158640d768f4.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:49:35', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 109),
(72, 'U2 L1: The Indus Valley – Urban Planning and Trade', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on the<strong> Indus Valley Civilization</strong> introduces early city planning in Harappa and Mohenjo-Daro, with straight roads, drains, and mud-brick houses.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Build a Mini Grid drawing task, Clean City Challenge, and What Would You Trade?</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of sanitation, fair trade, and the lasting legacy of ancient urban planning.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 631, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756547507355-68b2ef9e-e50c-4cb2-934d-4e471d737446.pptx', 'SS_G5_U2_L1.pptx', 4583645, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756547507369-7a11c92f-13cf-474e-ae3b-1766c17d8d0d.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:51:47', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 108),
(73, 'U2 L2: Ancient China – Inventions and Economic Growth', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Ancient China</strong> introduces major dynasties such as the Han, Tang, and Song, highlighting inventions like silk, paper, printing, the compass, and gunpowder.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: What’s in Your Trade Bag? drawing task, and Draw a Helpful Landform activity to connect geography with innovation.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of trade along the Silk Road, appreciation of Chinese contributions, and the role of geography in shaping civilizations.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 631, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756547621007-5dd2e252-c9ae-4a3d-ab41-69d6a504c1b2.pptx', 'SS_G5_U2_L2.pptx', 3733167, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756547621022-38a04daf-4f89-4ebe-a320-107160522031.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:53:41', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 107),
(74, 'U3 L1: Government and Society in Early Empires', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Government in Early Empires</strong> explains how civilizations like Mesopotamia, Egypt, and China developed rulers, laws, and systems to keep society safe and fair.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Think-Pair-Share on leadership, Fair Leader Checklist, and My Law Poster task.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of justice, fairness, and the role of leadership in building strong societies.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 631, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756547740686-3d087b33-dad9-410a-adf8-4cbbff2e8fae.pptx', 'SS_G5_U3_L1.pptx', 13142044, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756547741465-56fad7d2-7dc4-420a-8173-10358bad3f06.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 02:55:41', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 106),
(75, 'U3 L2: Cultural Exchange and Influence Between Civilizations', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Cultural Exchange</strong> explains how ideas, inventions, languages, and religions spread through travel and trade, helping civilizations grow.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Beliefs That Unite Us task and My Invention Passport project.</p></li><li><p>Promotes appreciation of writing systems, shared values across religions, technological progress, and peaceful cooperation among civilizations.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 631, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756548242304-10b86742-d7a5-4b80-8ee8-045f232aeb9f.pptx', 'SS_G5_U3_L2.pptx', 3361925, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756548242313-8d5fb6d1-2565-4507-96a6-980f668f8413.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 03:04:02', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 105),
(76, 'U4 L1: Mountains, Rivers, and Deserts', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Physical Features</strong> introduces students to mountains, rivers, and deserts, showing how these landforms shape life, survival, and history.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Landform Spotting Challenge, Mountain Living Sketch, River Path Relay, and Desert Survival Kit.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of natural environments, adaptation, and how landforms work together to support people, animals, and trade.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 631, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756548338328-f61367fe-42de-4600-acc8-4e19b68bb0b9.pptx', 'SS_G5_U4_L1.pptx', 7319973, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756548338356-6a2e800f-8499-423f-bf68-1536a0cc941f.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 03:05:38', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 104),
(77, 'U4 L2: Human-Environment Interaction', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Human-Environment Interaction</strong> explains how people adapt to mountains, rivers, and deserts, and how they also change the land through farming, building, and technology.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Draw “Me in My Environment,” Nature Hero or Hurter sorting game, and Build a Mini Eco-Village sketch.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of sustainable living, environmental responsibility, and Islamic values of balance and care for nature.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 631, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756548407829-9708cfde-44aa-4db1-9053-2c932691e5cd.pptx', 'SS_G5_U4_L2.pptx', 2443730, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756548407847-f501bba5-7f88-4099-b0e5-eb4c0a9bc90f.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 03:06:47', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 103),
(78, 'U1 L1: The Greek and Roman Empires', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on the<strong> Greek and Roman Empires</strong> introduces the geography, governance, and cultural achievements of ancient Greece and Rome.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Role-Play the Ancient Assembly (Athens vs. Rome) and Design Your Own City-State or Republic project.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of democracy and republics, appreciation of philosophy, law, and architecture, and awareness of their lasting impact on modern societies.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 632, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756549836896-15e8fa72-894b-4090-98fa-6a4f3808d726.pptx', 'SS_G6_U1_L1.pptx', 24760867, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756549839261-1add4890-4789-48b5-90cb-38356f49d412.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 03:30:39', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 102),
(79, 'U1 L2: The Islamic Golden Age', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>The Islamic Golden Age</strong> explores the period from the 8th to 14th century, highlighting centers of knowledge in Baghdad, Cairo, and Cordoba, and the work of scholars such as Al-Khwarizmi, Ibn Sina, and Ibn al-Haytham.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Quick Quiz checks, Journal of Insights reflection, and discussions on how the House of Wisdom compares to the internet today.</p></li><li><p>Promotes appreciation of Islamic contributions to science, medicine, mathematics, and navigation, and their lasting impact on the modern world.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 632, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756550123151-6adcacb7-88e1-45d6-afc1-a2d75012bf7b.pptx', 'SS_G6_U1_L2.pptx', 49219248, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756550128853-c3ba2e6e-3b31-4aaf-a0e5-c574f174497b.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 03:35:28', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 101),
(80, 'U1 L3: African Kingdoms – Ghana, Mali, and Songhai', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>African Kingdoms</strong> introduces the rise and achievements of Ghana, Mali, and Songhai, highlighting geography, trade, leadership, and centers of learning like Timbuktu.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: map discussions, multiple-choice and short-answer questions, and exploration of the gold-salt trade and Timbuktu’s libraries.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of Africa’s rich history, the value of trade, and the role of Islamic scholarship in shaping global knowledge.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 632, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756550263900-ed196dbc-1404-472a-955b-508a0dcd6c30.pptx', 'SS_G6_U1_L3.pptx', 11832960, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756550264501-3b5a629d-0834-49c6-8ef2-d472f0a31005.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 03:37:44', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 100),
(82, 'U2 L1: Feudalism and Monarchy in Europe', '<ul><li><p></p></li></ul><ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Feudalism and Monarchy</strong> introduces the structure of medieval European society, showing how kings, lords, knights, and serfs relied on each other for land, loyalty, and protection.</p></li><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Feudal Pyramid role-play, Loyalty Chain Craft, and Comparing Monarchies chart activity.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of hierarchy, loyalty as the foundation of society, and comparison between European and Saudi systems of monarchy.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 632, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756550439680-8a458fd0-7182-4d7e-ad32-899660bf3537.pptx', 'SS_G6_U2_L1.pptx', 15408474, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756550440771-a5cbe9d3-3ad6-435f-b729-99b5ba88cc1d.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 03:40:40', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 99),
(83, 'U2 L2: The Magna Carta and Its Legacy', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>The Magna Carta</strong> explains how King John of England was forced to sign the charter in 1215, limiting his power and protecting people’s rights.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Write about one important right, and Fun Fact exploration of the Magna Carta’s history and influence.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of the “Rule of Law,” fairness, and justice, while comparing Magna Carta principles with Islamic governance in Saudi Arabia.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 632, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756550591929-ca713272-eaf5-4b25-acd7-9fec888060ba.pptx', 'SS_G6_U2_L2.pptx', 22387589, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756550593966-bc3db543-4577-4937-96df-1682c519917e.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 03:43:14', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 98),
(84, 'U3 L1: The Silk Road and Global Trade', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>The Silk Road</strong> explores how goods, ideas, and cultures traveled across Asia, Arabia, and Europe through one of history’s greatest trade routes.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Trader’s Diary role-play and quiz questions to check understanding.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of Saudi Arabia’s central role in trade, the spread of Islam, and how supply and demand shaped global connections.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 632, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756551065780-27476c03-c1e6-4997-b78f-4cbe1e8005f7.pptx', 'SS_G6_U3_L1.pptx', 58303990, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756551072712-a139e81e-81e3-4e44-a4de-7226ccb60046.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 03:51:12', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 97),
(85, 'U3 L2: Mercantilism and the Age of Exploration', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Mercantilism and Exploration</strong> explains how European nations sought wealth, land, and trade routes through sea voyages during the Age of Exploration.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: “If I Were an Explorer” diary entry and quiz questions to test understanding.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of the impact on the Arabian Peninsula, the role of supply and demand in global trade, and both positive and negative outcomes of exploration.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 632, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756551440186-b48fba82-d5db-4533-8838-3b3ef8877bad.pptx', 'SS_G6_U3_L2.pptx', 65640711, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756551448121-18779147-816c-4654-b2b5-e62c1d9b923a.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 03:57:28', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 96),
(86, 'U4 L1: The Geography of Natural Resources', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Natural Resources</strong> explains renewable and non-renewable resources, their uneven distribution, and their role in shaping settlements and economies.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Sort It Out! classification task and Resource Detective cause-and-effect puzzle.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of Saudi Arabia’s resources (oil, gas, minerals, solar energy), global resource management, and sustainable use through Vision 2030.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 632, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756551728972-aa6a0231-2711-407a-82ff-cda428c6f737.pptx', 'SS_G6_U4_L1.pptx', 4617980, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756551729000-01db24ce-6986-4c35-8afb-fd55aec5857e.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 04:02:09', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 95),
(87, 'U4 L2: Human Adaptation and Modification in Different Environments', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on <strong>Human-Environment Interaction</strong> explores how people adapt to deserts, mountains, and cold regions, and how they modify their surroundings for survival.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: Problem Solver scenario, exploring qanats and desalination, and reviewing Vision 2030 projects like Green Riyadh, Haramain Railway, and Red Sea Project.</p></li><li><p>Promotes awareness of adaptation, sustainable living, and Saudi Arabia’s balance of tradition and modern solutions.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 632, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756551813850-1cfc13c6-94f5-4b38-b080-81a9a5a7b101.pptx', 'SS_G6_U4_L2.pptx', 2770002, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756551813859-faf7e84c-ab2f-4b9f-8d20-01b1809a5f31.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 04:03:33', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 94),
(88, 'U1 L1: The Persian Empire', '<ul><li><p>This presentation on the Persian Empire introduces Cyrus the Great, Darius I, the satrapy system of governance, and innovations such as the Royal Road, canals, and coinage.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Includes interactive activities: King’s Eyes and Ears role-play, Persian Empire Mapping Challenge, and Comparing Governance Systems chart.</p></li><li><p>Promotes understanding of governance, cultural exchange, and lessons from Persia’s legacy compared with modern systems, including Saudi Arabia.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 366, 436, 633, 1, 'backend/uploads/1756553212936-4785e1a5-c5c2-47c9-b342-163ee298c4a1.pptx', 'SS_G7_U1_L1.pptx', 14954351, 'pptx', 'backend/uploads/1756553213971-fefff988-37bd-4499-b99c-0ec534c66c55.png', 'draft', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2025-08-30 04:26:54', '2025-09-02 01:41:13', 93);
